# Production Docs Protection Rule

- Treat `/docs/Production/` as protected, high-importance operator documentation.
- Do not create, edit, move, or delete files under `/docs/Production/` unless the user gives an explicit command to do so.
- When changes are explicitly requested:
  - keep scope minimal and command-focused,
  - use real stack names and script paths from this repository,
  - include rollout and rollback commands.
- Any `/docs/Production/` change must also update:
  - `/docs/README.md`,
  - `.cursor/notes/task_log.md`,
  - `.cursor/notes/task_index.md`.
